de.esoco.lib.datatype

Enum DateRange.StandardDateRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DateRange.StandardDateRange>
      • de.esoco.lib.datatype.DateRange.StandardDateRange
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DateRange.StandardDateRange>
    Enclosing class:
    DateRange

    public static enum DateRange.StandardDateRange
extends java.lang.Enum<DateRange.StandardDateRange>
    An enumeration of typical date range types for date calculations and display in user interfaces. The value NONE has only a declarative purpose (e.g. for UI selection) and must not be used as an argument to methods like DateRange.calculateFor(StandardDateRange).
